plot: When Jane Quimby applies for a high-school internship at a major fashion house, a clerical snafu lands her a lucrative dream job as a part-time assistant to a demanding, globe-trotting fashion designer who goes through assistants like water. Will Jane be able to juggle the demands of high school and those of an adult fashion design assistant without anyone catching on?
title: "Jane by Design" Pilot
